summary: Welcome to Star Wars, Matt Smith
body:
Welcome to Star Wars, Matt Smith

It’s been announced that Matt Smith is going to be in the next Star Wars movie. Currently, we don’t know much/ anything about his character, so here are a few theories.

1.) He’s part of the Resistance

• Comes to help/ ends up helping them out after the events of TLJ

2.) He’s part of the First Order

• New officer who makes everyone’s lives difficult (or maybe just Hux’s)

• New general to replace Hux after he (finally) got promoted to Grand Marshal

3.) He’s a Knight of Ren

4.) He’s a double-agent

summary: Some of the first words spoken in TFA is Lor San Tekka addressing Kylo Ren and in his words he says "The First Order rose from...
body:
Some of the first words spoken in TFA is Lor San Tekka addressing Kylo Ren and in his words he says “The First Order rose from the darkside you did not”

And that’s a chunk of knowledge dropped in the first five minutes of the film that slowly has come unraveling. Ben Solo will save himself from Kylo Ren :)
